{
  "message": "test(conformance): add polynomial metamorphic cases (+12)\n\nPolynomial metamorphic relations (12 cases):\n- poly_add_zero_identity: p + 0 = p\n- poly_sub_self_zero: p - p = 0\n- poly_mul_one_identity: p * 1 = p\n- poly_deriv_integral_inverse: d/dx(integral(p)) = p\n- poly_add_commutative: a + b = b + a\n- poly_mul_commutative: a * b = b * a\n- poly_eval_linearity: eval(alpha*a + beta*b, x) = alpha*eval(a,x) + beta*eval(b,x)\n- poly_double_derivative_consistent: deriv(deriv(p)) vs deriv(p, 2)\n\nCoverage across all 5 polynomial families (polynomial1d, chebyshev, legendre, hermite, laguerre).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
